text: Oscar Hamrén (19 September 1891 - 10 April 1960) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1960 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Swedish male breaststroke swimmers
